ap gaming holdco inc private company information  bloomberg july    pm et leisure products company overview of ap gaming holdco inc snapshot people company overview ap gaming holdco inc designs and supplies gaming equipment and products for the gaming industry the company offers electronic gaming machines such as slot machines ancillary table game equipment and serverbased and backoffice systems for casinos and gaming locations additionally it provides installing maintenance and training services ap gaming holdco inc was founded in  and is headquartered in las vegas nevada  south decatur boulevardsuite las vegas nv united statesfounded in  phone  key executives for ap gaming holdco inc mr david b lopez chief executive officer president  director age  mr kimo akiona cfo chief accounting officer  treasurer age  mr victor j gallo general counsel  secretary age  compensation as of fiscal year  ap gaming holdco inc key developments ap gaming holdco inc announces executive changes may   ap gaming holdco inc appointed mr daniel cohen and mr david lopez as members of the companys board of directors effective may   mr cohen and mr lopez fill two of the vacancies on the board created by increasing the total number of directors constituting the board to three  directors mr david sambur will now assume the role of chairman of the board contemporaneous with his appointment to the board mr lopez resigned as secretary of the company mr vic gallo will now assume the duties of the company’s secretary in addition to his role as general counsel of the company the board voted to appoint mr kimo akiona as the chief financial officer and chief accounting officer of the company effective may   mr akiona’s duties and compensation which are set out in the  k will not change as a result of this new appointment ap gaming holdco inc announces auditor changes jul   the board of directors of the ap gaming holdco inc appointed pricewaterhousecoopers llp as the company’s independent registered pub